{
  "question": "what language pairs are explored?",
  "text": "The examined Europarl language configurations are French-English-Spanish (Fr-En-Es), German-English-French (De-En-Fr), and Romanian-English-German (Ro-En-De). English is the pivot language; the language to its left is the source and the language to its right is the target. Thus, the stated source-to-target directions are French\u2192English and English\u2192Spanish, German\u2192English and English\u2192French, and Romanian\u2192English and English\u2192German. [1]",
